{"tid":1181363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「大戰」而家啲甲由真係進化晒","createTime":"2019-06-01T14:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T15:35:06.000Z","uid":220068,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dd05af401e7dbfb879c0fa5c2ca2941ef1c9a7a2","tid":1181363,"uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"搵拖鞋落重手拍咗佢幾吓 以為咁就搞掂 點知呢個先係漫漫長夜既開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵野撩佢佢冇反應唔郁確認死咗<br />\n跟手搵掃把烏低身掃佢入鏟 點知隻野原來扮死 突然復活飛上黎<br />\n嗰刻我真係差啲就同佢kiss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我緊係即刻衝出房 見佢走入櫃底隙 個櫃又太大搬唔開 於是就灰機放棄狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知原來係埋伏黎 佢等我入黎又搞9我<br />\n當我心灰意冷又想入去瞓嗰陣 佢又飛出黎<br />\n我想講呢個物種真係好勁 佢地係識認人同會報仇 我一入房佢就飛落我度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱房有啲紙袋膠袋擺喺地 天網恢恢 我隨手又抄起拖鞋將隻野拍咗落其中一個袋度！<br />\n我即刻封起個袋 本身想倒落廁所 但驚倒嗰吓佢又飛出黎<br />\n跟住我就搵掃把瘋狂插佢隊佢 但隻野完全乜事都冇<br />\n把掃把明明啲毛好尖好硬吓 只可以話而家啲甲由真係進化咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有裝甲加成<br />\n只好直接倒落廁所 點知更恐怖既係 佢識游水同爬返上黎 仲識lei喺隱閉既馬桶邊<br />\n我唔即時沖廁係想睇佢有幾頑強 用花灑噴返佢落去<br />\n點知喺高壓既水沖撃之下 隻野不但冇沖走仲可以繼續向上爬<br />\n最後惟有開大花灑+沖廁 先正式了結咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位記住整返支殺蟲傍身 純物理攻擊+捉真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2ab341ad09a8c106c67b580b745d522b7e1bc2","tid":1181363,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"Okay thx"},{"pid":"9f55c545d5de89cf90974db3c9e4492daf9f7cb5","tid":1181363,"uid":242064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0adcf038aa26ee8a4fa266cdd8909ae570839f9","tid":1181363,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"近排落雨<br />\n琴晚有隻我人生中見過最巨型既強<br />\n係窗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛</span>左入屋<br />\n點解甲由可以咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a27722c2b7d84d081ac59d5612071a9a5aadde5","tid":1181363,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"依排我係廁所用剃鬚膏殺甲由 <br />\n一野噴落佢個身到 一陣就反肚"},{"pid":"720cf92345bb00cd3a5b7e3d26f00afce368d6a1","tid":1181363,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"誠收神獸男女各一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a44feca39a648a7ff83d85483761f47f654bd6d","tid":1181363,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"以為你用掃把棍隊都隊唔死咁勁<br />\n屌你用個刷頭果邊隊佢把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9e8158df4168072a3ac8bae605fc0cf8a9baa3","tid":1181363,"uid":201356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a27722c2b7d84d081ac59d5612071a9a5aadde5","tid":1181363,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"依排我係廁所用剃鬚膏殺甲由 <br />\n一野噴落佢個身到 一陣就反肚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"番梘水洗潔精嗰啲有化學屬性<br />\n可以抵銷裝甲 無孔不入給予致命一擊<br />\n<br />\nbtw小強識游水是常識吧 浸成個鐘都未死"},{"pid":"a6c6cf30c9d008563bcf0c55a73338b3adf2d55b","tid":1181363,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"宜家曱甴反應好快。搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n結果都係用藥"},{"pid":"bf8a0bb95aeaf08a8c6c01641556303c27cf8544","tid":1181363,"uid":178714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"我試過倒天拿水落隻甲由度<br />\n即刻反肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo