rc=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9508e63fb9b2361d6eb6d6dedf8c76dc48df2c0f","tid":1181363,"uid":46342,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男人老狗驚隻曱甴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋係曱甴 唔係甲由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76ac7c9f16065b6b9c34a6638c0e7e4b2e4d737","tid":1181363,"uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4444df578d0088f0b70c710961dffa1d933bb85a","tid":1181363,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"一個如來神掌就扁哂啦，邊會仲識走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"拍扁佢只會入面啲bb同汁液爆出黎 到時仲煩"},{"pid":"eedb88fa84c5d85afda54cc053565958b3e0dc81","tid":1181363,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"又呢樣又果樣，踩死佢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043a293e79e192e4d00bff7bb1bf18f9eaa3eb2d","tid":1181363,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"咁啱房有啲紙袋膠袋擺喺地<br />\n<br />\n你屋企係咪好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚甲甴就最好唔好咁多雜物喇"},{"pid":"24945c50a4774d8096250130fdf94a7077a85a9f","tid":1181363,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"你確定佢真係死咗？<br />\n陣間你開大嗰陣會唔會游返上嚟捐你菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj